0.1 -> 0.2

* Fixed Failure to update previous line buffer when user entered a line number
at command mode. Now it is initialized to contents of current line.

0.2 -> 0.3

* Now compiles clean on both Linux and Freebsd
* Ported to Freebsd (Needed new _HARDCH makefile define. See last section of
  readme.)
* Now restores terminal settings on exit 
* Added extensive background discussions on terminals to the README
* Corrections to man page
* Corrections to key maps and added one for FreeBsd
* Added a wrapper script for FreeBsd
* Corrected display of Tab character when previous line is recalled
* Numerous other bug fixes


